{"tid":1538010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警告你班冷氣兒登仔咪撚再看圖捉鬼","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T14:17:14.000Z","uid":39752,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfecd693ce485d48440c78288a25e368f3dfe90","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人阻止到你班冷氣兒登仔捉鬼，就算你哋唔捉，fb 啲村民都會懶醒咁捉</span></strong><br />\n但可唔可以唔好見到件裝備<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">專業少少</span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好似有記認</span></strong>就話係鬼<br />\n<br />\n基本邏輯題：<br />\n落雨地下就會濕，咁見到地下濕係咪一定代表落咗雨？<br />\n同樣道理：<br />\n啲鬼會用某啲裝備，咁見到某啲裝備係咪一定係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重未計你哋根本認錯晒啲「裝備」？<br />\n記唔記得有手足幾個鐘頭俾人當咗四次速龍？<br />\n記唔記得你哋好開心喺度捉粉紅色記號，最後捉錯屠龍隊？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n手槍汽油彈單嘢為例<br />\n人話 CTRU 配 Glock 17，你哋又跟住講 Glock 17<br />\n 部隊用嘅槍都係全黑，點會突然有一支沙色嘅走出嚟？<br />\n現場搵到同一隻彈殼就代表係 exactly 嗰支沙色 glock 射嘅？俾返少少邏輯好唔好？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事實就係有配槍嘅可能係鬼，亦有可能唔係，因為你睇相唔會判斷到係真定係玩具<br />\n單憑一支槍就話係鬼嘅話，你即係叫緊手足以後唔好帶鬼火出去</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n又例如呢啲鳩 post 連戰術頭盔條路軌都唔知係乜嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535017/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535017/page/1</a><br />\n咁撚樣就八百幾正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />常識 where are you？？？<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔想有任何人因為真係有鬼而懶醒咁亂咁捉鬼<br />\n手足帶支可能係鬼火嘅氣槍又捉，戰術頭盔又捉，組隊帶燈又捉<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人講你又講，有幾多人對呢啲裝備有認識<br />\n鬼會帶嗰啲裝備，唔代表自己人就唔會</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真係要捉鬼，現場手足走去打個招呼都可靠過你班冷氣兒登仔</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而就算你捉到嗰啲係乜嘢狗狗用緊呀同款呀咁又點？<br />\n有啲根本就係民用品嚟，要買唔難，拎出嚟用更加唔出奇<br />\n例如呢隻頭盔直情係水上運動用嘅，防禦力太好連香港狗狗都有入貨<br />\n<a href=\"https://protecbrand.com/collections/ace-water/products/ace-water-matte-black-2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprotecbrand.com%2Fcollections%2Face-water%2Fproducts%2Face-water-matte-black-2017&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=96330dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://protecbrand.com/collections/ace-water/products/ace-water-matte-black-2017</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akFcP1x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakFcP1x.png&h=39488db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如呢個眼罩你分唔分到同 SDU 用緊嗰啲有乜分別？<br />\nHKTV 都有得賣喎MIL-PRF 32432 係美軍防彈標準喎？<br />\n分唔到？因為佢真係 SDU CTRU RRT 都用緊嗰隻囉，鏡片唔同色咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E5%BE%B7%E6%B3%B0%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/H6663001/%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%99%A8/%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%99%A8/%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%8E%E8%A6%96-IFORCE-SLIM-%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%B7%E7%9B%AE%E7%9C%BC%E9%8F%A1/p/H6663001_S_PYSB7020SDNT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktvmall.com%2Fhktv%2Fzh%2Fmain%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%2Fs%2FH6663001%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2599%25A8%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2599%25A8%2F%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2593%2581%2F%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BB%2596%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A6%2596-IFORCE-SLIM-%25E7%2581%25B0%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259C%25BC%25E9%258F%25A1%2Fp%2FH6663001_S_PYSB7020SDNT&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=eaa745c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E5%BE%B7%E6%B3%B0%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/H6663001/%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%99%A8/%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%99%A8/%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%8E%E8%A6%96-IFORCE-SLIM-%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E8%AD%B7%E7%9B%AE%E7%9C%BC%E9%8F%A1/p/H6663001_S_PYSB7020SDNT</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdqDLB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdqDLB7.jpg&h=ad32e086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軍品定係民用仿製品你睇相又唔會分到<br />\n手足為咗怕你哋捉鬼，就一齊用返垃圾硬膠地盤帽泳鏡咁樣好無？<br />\n到時啲鬼唔識一齊轉返硬膠地盤帽咩？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根本就係你哋自己唔鍾意、唔識、覺得太勁嘅就係鬼<br />\n手足就應該用垃圾，勁裝就一定係狗？<br />\n一世地盤帽勞工手套迪卡儂就一定無鬼啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁所有會跌勁裝出街嘅物資組係咪應該收一收皮先？原來會累咗手足呀陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049dc4d45128395b893ceb3553c8a7132056444e","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:09:39.000Z","msg":"自推一百次"},{"pid":"adf01e7f2ef4691bf848833ac58151ed1fc4b4d6","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"自推99次"},{"pid":"8221efe284c6f6892be3012d6cfa7e2215dcb57e","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"自推98次"},{"pid":"2d2f9d907bf5adc4215c23cdea4a719b4d80607a","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"自推97次"},{"pid":"89a2020354d9ab5d78c599571af72fd646f55c1c","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"自推96次"},{"pid":"4bf8828f322b8bb8977bf466715abc9a559dbc8c","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"自推95次"},{"pid":"1ddcf32e6c2ac17f738c3382c201d43477ee8d34","tid":1538010,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"斷你自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44883e452391729125ae27c549765fc99c858c1","tid":1538010,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"一定要推爆"},{"pid":"b500b6cd34df9672a0bd95f5bf1113fd549d8e8c","tid":1538010,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"成班人自己on9就算，最大個問題係唔用係有用地方身上，用係有勇有謀既手足身上"},{"pid":"03e3956c0f7ab057af5ae736aa1eaa106a48a041","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f96a8bbbabf621cddb8d5358e6c0810cd42e9cc","tid":1538010,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"人呢，有建設性既野又唔入黎"},{"pid":"a83f0fabd774ca01bf9fe6edf9c2c33c471a7caa","tid":1538010,"uid":230954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"f67425521f97aa4aeabb00c85a87ab2f55704769","tid":1538010,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46dce41a734adba27555c28db3c8fb0f28eb1420","tid":1538010,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"Tui<br />\n<br />\n有關破壞<br />\n<br />\n公物係用公帑，叫工人整。圍差館係送上門比差人除暴安良。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好學惡霸美國，搞阻礙香港民主進程官員嘅財產！<br />\n<br />\n勇武千祈唔好破壞私物！特別係某啲人嘅私物，財產，公司，物業。人地仲要claim保險點告到你班仆街暴動！<br />\n<br />\n和理非千祈唔好係唔犯法嘅情況令啲嘢貶值，例如唔小心跌左啲好臭嘅嘢，識郁嘅嘢。黑材料，桃色糾紛乜乜乜啊。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好！<br />\n<br />\n特別係唔好hit and run! 好衰！"},{"pid":"5715947fc6e0f25adf0f031b27e898ffaa87d930","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5e83e0a015e398f19b795525a26e87be4cd829","tid":1538010,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:08:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33fade8792717f615dd8437b644229df0121567","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"幫我貼去每一個捉鬼 post 下面好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a2b1085c0cdeb0cdb2aa05b5a45ef50071723d","tid":1538010,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33fade8792717f615dd8437b644229df0121567","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"幫我貼去每一個捉鬼 post 下面好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1df7ec7a71a72203275c732353f797d679dc24","tid":1538010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cc1c3af2ce4d99a467f72410014c470f58e0fa","tid":1538010,"uid":254581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"你鬼火極都唔會夠力架啦，帶去做乜"},{"pid":"4643edf214dd8a594faff427dc72d28d751cf26e","tid":1538010,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4485456ab1f4b663dc5aef26815d8c4cdeafe1c0","tid":1538010,"uid":281293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1b809b233c39a45dcb42fc6fa306583a0e6c8e","tid":1538010,"uid":241249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:10:11.000Z","msg":"推爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c808e43a79cdf6de99fd79b91d2f48544bca4cf","tid":1538010,"uid":38204,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"兒登捉鬼又點 都係喺冷氣房捉 又唔會真係落場捉<br />\n捉啱定錯都唔會影響到 反而會俾到人錯覺啲事端係由鬼帶頭做"}]}